---
title: "US60 — Manage feedback + contact messages"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Administrator
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>FeedbackScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>TriageFeedback
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Feedback · ContactMessage
  A->>B: open feedback inbox
  B->>C: loadFeedback()
  C->>E: listFeedback()
  E-->>C: List of Feedback + ContactMessage
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (inbox)
  A->>B: tap Mark Reviewed / Resolved
  B->>C: setStatus(feedbackId, status)
  C->>E: updateFeedbackStatus(feedbackId, status)
  E-->>C: Feedback (updated status)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (updated)
  B-->>A: queue cleared
  note over E: listFeedback / updateFeedbackStatus via SupabaseGateway (RLS admin-only).<br/>user-side SubmitFeedback writes via FeedbackGateway.submitFeedback
